             was indicted for <rs id="t18170917-11-off58" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170917-11-off58" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170917-11-off58" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
